default5.1.
default&#xa0; 
defaultThe number of academies whose performance causes concern is a very small percentage of the total.
default5.2.
default&#xa0; 
defaultThe current mechanism of issui
defaultng sponsors with pre warning notices and, if subsequently necessary, warning letters, has led to considerable and quick improvements in these academies.
default5.3.
default&#xa0; 
defaultIn extreme circumstances, where it is considered that standards are unlikely to rise quickly enough, it
