default6.1.
default&#xa0; 
defaultLocal authorities should: 
defaultprovide the 
defaultstrategic 
defaultvision for the 
defaulteconomic and social 
defaultdevelopment of their defined local area; set key goals; identify challenges
default;
default and provide the framework within which all education and training providers can eff
defaultectively operate in partnership
