default8.1.
default&#xa0; 
defaultAcademy status is equally relevant to primary schools as it is to secondary schools and growth in the numbers of primary academies should be supported 
defaultand encouraged.
default8.2.
default&#xa0; 
defaultAcademy status represents a particular mind-set and approach to leadership and management, 
defaultwhere 
defaultcomplete responsibility for the performance of one’s own organisation is adopted and therefore 
defaultacademisation
default is appropriate for any school, irr
defaultespective of age phase or size.
