defaults that come with academy status, difficulties in creating a high reliability organisation (given the increa
defaultsed likelihood of key person dependency) and the sustainability of leadership
default. 
default8.4.
default&#xa0; 
defaultTherefore, cluster arrangements are sometimes appropriate and are often most effective when one or more outstanding school is part of the group.
